{"type": "article", "id": 22516, "title": "圆环桌灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122539bfk1lro2nyJxWsVH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏像圆环一样的桌灯来自芬兰设计工作室 himmee，最早出现在 2009 年的米兰家具展上，最近完成了工业化并出现在斯德哥尔摩家具展上。它其实是铝制的，光源在环状灯内壁的上半侧。点亮后整盏灯就像是一根舞动的带子，很有意境。有黑白两色可选，售价 419 欧元，<a href=\"http://himmee.com/product/loop/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122536fxmUQtI2e7EXsu6l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122537DhveCl0jrRHaQmL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49633252\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122537XsKlSL9obF3CRnqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61735941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122538fZiOwcCm0xh6Ttz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}